{"pageProps":{"post":{"attributes":{},"html":"<p>In the Model folder we will create some manager objects that will be used as singletons in our app</p>\n<h2 id=\"menumanager\">MenuManager</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-swift\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MenuManager</span> {    \n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> menu: [<span class=\"hljs-type\">Category</span>] <span class=\"hljs-operator\">=</span> [] \n}\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"cartmanager\">CartManager</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-swift\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">CartManager</span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> products: [(<span class=\"hljs-type\">Product</span>, <span class=\"hljs-type\">Int</span>)] <span class=\"hljs-operator\">=</span> []\n        \n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">product</span>: <span class=\"hljs-type\">Product</span>, <span class=\"hljs-params\">quantity</span>: <span class=\"hljs-type\">Int</span>) {\n        products.append((product, quantity))\n    }\n        \n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">remove</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">product</span>: <span class=\"hljs-type\">Product</span>) {\n        products.removeAll { productInCart <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span>\n            productInCart.<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>.id <span class=\"hljs-operator\">==</span> product.id\n        }\n    }\n    \n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">clear</span>() {\n        products.removeAll()\n    }\n    \n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">total</span>() -&gt; <span class=\"hljs-type\">Double</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> total <span class=\"hljs-operator\">=</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.0</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> item <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">in</span> products {\n            total <span class=\"hljs-operator\">+=</span> item.<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>.price <span class=\"hljs-operator\">*</span> <span class=\"hljs-type\">Double</span>(item.<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n        }\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> total\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n","slug":"creating-data-managers","title":"Creating Data Managers","section":"Working with Data","icon":"database","filePath":"/home/runner/work/intro-swift/intro-swift/lessons/05-working-with-data/B-creating-data-managers.md","nextSlug":"/intro-swift/lessons/working-with-data/using-environment-objects","prevSlug":"/intro-swift/lessons/working-with-data/creating-model"}},"__N_SSG":true}